{"tid":2343801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"12港人送中︱突改公開審訊　法院指旁聽名額已滿　多國外交官被拒旁聽","createTime":"2020-12-28T08:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T10:58:51.000Z","uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5bca54d0edaf47541af7504ab518e13622786ba3","tid":2343801,"uid":271829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:15:37.000Z","msg":"...<br />\n（更新：內容）12名涉及反修例運動案件的香港青年，被內地指涉嫌偷越邊境，其中10名被告今午2時半在深圳鹽田法院審訊，原先法院稱以視像方式開審，閉門聆訊，下午卻改稱案件依法公開審理，不過，有法院職員向《蘋果》指，今日旁聽席已滿，亦不會安排庭審直播。當局如臨大敵，在法院外加強保安。美國駐廣州總領事館今早發表聲明，指12港人是「逃避暴政」，要求中方放人，多國亦派代表到法院，希望入內旁聽，但至開廳時間，法院仍不准外交官進入。12名港人被拘留在內地至今已128日，從未獲與家屬或家屬委託的律師見面，家屬批評當局漠視眾人法律權利，令外界擔心眾人能否獲得合理的法律保障與公平審理。<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201228/67PMA7VJGFF4RCAQ2A6WV3MHC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201228%2F67PMA7VJGFF4RCAQ2A6WV3MHC4%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjdwWTNdVklcLtcNqJxXVG150%3D&h=86683371\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201228%2F67PMA7VJGFF4RCAQ2A6WV3MHC4%2F&h=418270de\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201228/67PMA7VJGFF4RCAQ2A6WV3MHC4/</a>"},{"pid":"18218d0782d460fe2912e54b96e01a6f8aa95eef","tid":2343801,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T08:29:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bf74218e508375bd5bb76141bdb6c56306ae971","tid":2343801,"uid":14494,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T10:56:18.000Z","msg":"陽光司法 公開審理 依法處理 保障人權<br />\n仲有幾多笑話？"},{"pid":"e52243e6435a994cf74a6026eb5b